I hope that you see it through

And squeeze me

(Ghostface)
Yeah
Yo we used to spin back ‚ÄúLovin‚Äô you‚Äù
Minnie Ripperton
The bose speakers had my walls and the plaques trembling
Lalala playing my mind all day

Bubble baths arose
Gucci open toes
Sunday nights we sitting watching Power in our robes

I just got up and walked in the room,
you still cussing

‚ÄúGoodnight‚Äùs is out the windows, it lasts for weeks

Promised to love you and hit two times a day never cheat now
Our chemistry is like a bowl of cherries,
and I‚Äôm the chocolate i smother you
Never to worry

And are you gonna love me
You‚Äôre gonna wanna hug me and squeeze me
(I‚Äôm gonna share half of the blame for this problem we are gonna through, you know i'm a taurus, the bull, i'm stubborn, so tell me what's on your mind) - Ghostface

Sometimes I don't think we really say enough
Why is it so hard to keep in touch
When we‚Äôre laying right next to each other, baby
We shouldn't read into things so much
Overthinking, understanding
Don't let a feeling change it up

I wanna spend my nights with you
My life with you, oh baby babe
Please wait up for me til whenever i get home
I know that I‚Äôm all alone
Thinking ‚Äòbout what i'm gon‚Äô do
I hope that i see it through, ooh, ooh, yeah

(Method Man) 
I ain't got time for tricks
Them broads aint loyal
I get a spanish chick, i make arroz con pollo
Keep my woman fresh
So she will never be spoiled
And she can be my queen, but we will never be royals
I don't give you cream, yadamean? But i assure you
I'm heavy with the d, i got nothing but love for you

Yeah if i adore you, mi amor you
These dudes cannot afford you, let the god couture you

Shorty got a receipt but her ex gets the bill
Look I'm too grown for netflix and chill

love me

Are you gonna love and squeeze me

(Raekwon)
Yeah man
You know what it is ma
Ay yo chef aka the wedding crasher
Came through in the Cullanin
Color of skim milk the wrath
Only us in the corner with the paid face, black cards and louis face
African cousins with us, we niggas
Smoking blunts, wine thats licatta

Now we here getting license
And i'm tired of the whole jack and jill shit, the real shit
Both of us comfortable now, so you ain't ever gotta feel shit
Feed a nigga laugh for hours
Count by ones, playing old school shit
While we fuck in the shower
And now you know your guard is top tier
Remember the message,
Love with capital letters until they dead us

snippet.title: Carla Makes Pasta e Fagioli | From the Test Kitchen | Bon App√©tit
snippet.description:
Join Carla in the Test Kitchen as she make pasta e fagioli! The key to a soup with fully developed savory flavor starts with the soffritto‚Äîa mix of aromatic vegetables that are slowly cooked in the first stage of cooking. Take your time sweating down the vegetables until they are completely softened before letting them take on any color. You‚Äôll be surprised by how much volume they lose and how much liquid they release and by how much unquantifiable richness they lend to the final dish, which is nothing more than a combination of humble ingredients. 
Did you notice the book Carla was holding at the beginning? That's her book! Buy it here: https://www.amazon.com/Where-Cooking-Begins-Uncomplicated-Recipes/dp/0525573348

snippet.title: TRADITIONAL STREET FOOD & Tofu Hotpot in Kyoto Japan
snippet.description:
Kyoto is one of my favorite cities in Japan with its beautiful traditional culture and of course the delicious foods. And for my first full day in Kyoto what's not a better thing to do than to go on a traditional street food tour in the area of Arashiyama. I also stopped by this tofu hotpot place, and it was an amazingly delicious experience. I loved the traditional Japanese style garden view as well which made it so relaxing while dining.
